node.text: Joe Biden knows what affordable healthcare means to American families because of what it’s meant to his.

node.text: I discuss family, childhood hunger, daddydaughterday.com and how proud I am of @isabellebridgesboesch with @nokidhungry’s @billshore on the #addpassionandstir podcast. Find it at addpassionandstir.com or wherever you get your podcasts. #socialjustice #socialgood #activism

node.text:
To mark National Book Day, we are giving away a signed copy of my photo book - 'Pictures Volume Two'. To enter follow @thejeffbridges and @joinsleepclub and tag a friend in this post. Share this in your story for an extra entry! 

Rules: Giveaway will be closed at 11:59 PM PST on 04/30/21. One winner will be selected and notified via Instagram direct message. No necessary purchase. Void where prohibited. Must be 18+ US residents only. This giveaway is in no way sponsored, endorsed or administered by, or associated with, Instagram.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jeff Bridges on March 30, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of 3 people and people standing.

node.text: I’m sorry to hear that the brilliant novelist and sceenwriter Larry McMurty passed away. I got to know him a bit when I was cast in THE LAST PICTURE SHOW, a movie that truly stands on its own.  Saying his words were easy because they were so real, they felt natural and it showed on the screen. All of us who worked on that film knew that we were making something special.  His writings brought out the gamut of emotions to all that were lucky to behold them.

node.text:
As the Dude would say.. New S**T has come to light. 

I have been diagnosed with Lymphoma. Although it is a serious disease, I feel fortunate that I have a great team of doctors and the prognosis is good. 

I’m starting treatment and will keep you posted on my recovery.

I’m profoundly grateful for the love and support from my family and friends.

Thank you for your prayers and well wishes.  And, while I have you, please remember to go vote. Because we are all in this together. Vote.org

Love, Jeff

node.text: My daughter, Isabelle, and I are in the new issue of @people. It hits newsstands this Friday. Got a chance to talk about our new book, Daddy Daughter Day.
